    <text>
        <body>
      
			<p><addressee>Rev&#58; Dr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#44; <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
          <p rend="indent(4)"><placeName>Claiborne Ala.</placeName> <date>May 1<hi rend="sup">st</hi> 1853</date>.</p>
			<p>Reverend Sir&#33;</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">It affords us pleasure to announce<lb/> that the Israelites of this small town have established<lb/> a Congregation under the name of <add>Hebrew</add> and at the meeting<lb/> of the Congregation held <date>April 26<hi rend="sup">th</hi></date> the following gentlemen were<lb/> elected officers for the ensuing year. <persName>Sal&#58; Levy Esq</persName> <sic>Presidend</sic><lb/> <persName>I. I. Rothshild</persName> Treasurer&#44; <persName>L. I. Herrman</persName>&#44; Trustee&#44; <persName role="author">A. Wolff</persName>&#44; Secretary<lb/> We are only 15 members in their Congregation and are glad<lb/> to let you know&#44; that <persName>Mr. Leopold Maas<add>&#63;</add></persName> a lately comer from<lb/> <placeName>Europe</placeName>&#44; has been chosen <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> On motion&#44; the following resolutions were unanimously<lb/> adopted</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Resolved&#44; that the thanks of the Congregation are due<lb/> and hereby tendered to the President and Board of Trustees&#44;<lb/> for the able and efficient manner in which the affairs of<lb/> this Congregation have been conducted</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Resolved. That the <del>thanks</del> congregation duly appreciates<lb/> the services rendered by the secretary</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Resolved That the proceedings be published in the Occident<lb/> &#40;Extract from the Minutes&#41;&#160;&#160;<persName role="author">A. Wolff Secretary</persName>.</p>
			<p></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Please send us the bill for inserting the above<lb/> and we will send you the remittance or pay the amount to your agent <persName role="author">Rev. B. M. Emanuel</persName>&#44; <placeName>Mobile Ala</placeName>.</p>
          
        </body>
